    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-cared for and still has tons of life left in it! Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is ready to roll. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
