      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp via individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This driver-focused example benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system, ensuring the variable valve timing remains precise across the 8,000 RPM powerband. The chassis retains its factory-tuned balance with a limited-slip M Differential Lock and MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and no signs of rod bearing fatigue. A quintessential analog experience for the discerning pilot.",
